What is debouncing?
:- Debouncing is technique to add deley in javascript event, function and component excution.

What is throttling?
:- throttling is technique to fire event after a partucler time from last event hitted.

Real use cases?
:- debouncing best use case is, when we implement search in input each strok then we add deley.
:- throttling best use case 

